item.title: CVE-2023-28053|2024-08-02T12:30:24.034Z -- dell -- networker%20virtual%20edition
item.description: Dell NetWorker Virtual Edition versions 19.8 and below contain the use of deprecated cryptographic algorithms in the SSH component. A remote unauthenticated attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability leading to some information disclosure.
